data.description: Stunning 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath home with oversized 2-Car Garage. This single level home boasts a gardener's paradise with exquisite gardens and lush vegetation, offering a serene oasis right in your backyard.Step into the sun room, a versatile space that's both heated and cooled, allowing you to enjoy it year-round.The primary suite is a haven of comfort, featuring a spacious walk-in closet, an updated shower, and double sinks. The bedrooms are generously proportioned, providing ample space for your needs.Entertaining is a breeze with the expanded Trex decking on the patio, providing a wonderful extension of your living space. Imagine hosting gatherings or simply relaxing in this inviting outdoor area. The family room delivers comfort and easy access through the slider to the AZ room.No HOA
